description:
This is a PSP version which has emulated perfectly on two different rigs without any issues using PPSSPP 8.1 GOLD; very simple to use.


Peace Walker consists of two primary playing modes: &quot;Mission&quot; and &quot;Mother Base&quot;. &quot;Mission&quot; are the actual action sequences of the game, 
where the player must infiltrate an enemy territory, whereas &quot;Mother Base&quot; is a crew managing simulation mode similar to the &quot;Comrade System&quot; in Portable Ops.

Extract with 7zip, or WinRAR. 

